product.name: Stainless Steel C Clamps 1.5 Inch for Working, Tiger Clamp Woodworking Clamp Heavy Duty C-clamp With Wide Jaw Openings for Woodworking Mounting Welding, 2 PCS
product.bullet_points:
• The protection pad of the mounting clamp can ensure the clamped object will not be easily deformed.
• The stainless steel C clamp is precision cast from high-quality 304 stainless steel, provides reliability, rust-proof, wear resistance and corrosion resistance.
• The clamping range is about 0.4-1.5 inches/10-38mm. Up to 1.37 inch throat depth.
• Can hang lights/ropes on metal truss.
